summary:
Hey guys! Have you ever wanted the chance to be in the magazine but were never sure how? Well now is your chance! 
To celebrate...
body:
Hey guys! Have you ever wanted the chance to be in the magazine but were never sure how? Well now is your chance! 

To celebrate the one year anniversary of Interactive Introverts we want you guys to send us some of your best memories/moments from your show! We’re going to make a special section in the magazine for this and we’ll try to include as many as we can!
